fr.cnrs.iees.graph

Packages that use fr.cnrs.iees.graph
Package
Description
fr.cnrs.iees.graph
The core interfaces of the omugi library: graph, node, edge, etc.
fr.cnrs.iees.graph.impl
Three implementations of the fr.cnrs.iees.graph interfaces.
fr.cnrs.iees.graph.io
Interfaces for graph importation from / exportation to text files.
fr.cnrs.iees.graph.io.impl
Implementations of GraphExporter and GraphImporter for various data formats.
fr.cnrs.iees.io
Classes to import / export graphs into data files of various formats.
fr.cnrs.iees.io.parsing
Interfaces for translating text into graph entities.
fr.cnrs.iees.io.parsing.impl
Implementing classes for interfaces of fr.cnrs.iees.io.parsing.
